reviews.author_name: Ro lan de ti kal fe Chong
reviews.text:
I love this outlet more than plq because there are more games suitable for my 4yo boy as compared to plq. And also the Chinese long black hair lady with specs is friendly, always makes me feel welcome whenever I bring my son there.

Definitely recommend to bring preschoolers for their games there.

Can someone here tell me whether Zone X T3 got the “ fish hunter” or “ fish hitting game”which has a rectangular table played by 6 or 8 persons at the same time. We will have some few hours at Changi airport before proceeding to K.L. Your information will be greatly appreciated.David.
